## Tailwind CSS v4 eliminates JavaScript config

Tailwind v4 (released January 2025) introduces **CSS-first configuration** using the `@theme` directive, eliminating `tailwind.config.js` for most projects:

```css
/* app/globals.css */
@import "tailwindcss";

@theme {
  --color-primary: oklch(0.53 0.12 118.34);
  --font-display: "Satoshi", sans-serif;
  --breakpoint-3xl: 1920px;
}
```

PostCSS setup is minimal with `@tailwindcss/postcss`:

```js
// postcss.config.mjs
export default {
  plugins: {
    '@tailwindcss/postcss': {},
  },
}
```

New features include **native container queries** (`@container`, `@sm:grid-cols-3`), **3D transforms** (`rotate-x-12`, `perspective-distant`), and **OKLCH gradients** with color space interpolation (`bg-linear-to-r/oklch`). Custom utilities now use `@utility` instead of `@layer utilities`.

